;; Kannada Composable Pattern
;;    C .. Consonants
;;    V .. Vowel
;;    H .. Virama
;;    M .. Matra
;;    V .. Vowel
;;    (N .. Zerowidth Non Joiner)
;;    (J .. Zerowidth Joiner.  )
;; 1. vowel
;;  V(A)?
;; 2. syllable : maximum of 5 consecutive consonants.  (e.g. kartsnya)
;;  ((CH)?(CH)?(CH)?CH)?C(H|M?)?

